collection.name: FormStack QA
collection.description:
Requirements
1. You must create a Formstack account (trial) if you haven’t already
2. You must create an API Application at our developers center
a. https://www.formstack.com/admin/apiKey/main
3. You must test the following API methods (all found under ‘Forms’):
	a. Get all forms on the account
	b. Get a specific form on the account
	c. Copy a form
	d. Delete the copied form
4. You can write your own tool using the Formstack API or use an existing tool
5. You must record the following for each test:
a. Request URL & query string
b. Response Code
c. Response (JSON)
6. You must write a test plan / test case for the tests to be ran.
